      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; iterative convergence monitoring is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, formal quantification of numerical solver error beyond iterative convergence monitoring is not required. Residuals were confirmed to reach 1e-5 for all transport equations at each operating point."
